{"tid":1191291,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《逃犯條例》一過，香港企業無晒保障，仲想同中資競爭？等收購/執凹啦！","createTime":"2019-06-07T23:19:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T07:07:22.000Z","uid":103513,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"499893751648d0e85abcb5aec97e430df12834de","tid":1191291,"uid":103513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T23:19:24.000Z","msg":"阿信屋仲想同優品360爭？人地同大陸嗰邊傾幾句就可以拉晒你班股東上去「接受調查」，睇下你啲貨有無違反支那法律<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n榮華，恆香咁好生意，班支那商人一早就流晒口水<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以後一係就乖乖地畀中資收購，一係就等畀差佬引渡返去支那調查「食品安全」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有其他啲中小企呀，唔好以為無你地份<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />純粹睇下有無支那商人睇中你盤生意，睇咗咗就係咁先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你地贏嘅機會係零呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw唔知到時仲有無香港人敢得罪你身邊啲支那同事呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n親，說不定人家跟深圳公安陳大隊長是同鄉喔？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc08c3266f0f08a173efa8c1d343183c65e800c8","tid":1191291,"uid":103513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T23:21:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"114c777287c9d71f5ad3a5b1a4043e06ac7a2233","tid":1191291,"uid":103513,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T23:24:53.000Z","msg":"以後條街得返阿信360<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4a07043f883f7af6a7f4a15ad7ce19d2e9fe4fc","tid":1191291,